.SH "NAME"
cdist-type__rvm \- Install rvm for a given user
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.sp
RVM is the Ruby enVironment Manager for the Ruby programming language\&.
.SH "REQUIRED PARAMETERS"
.PP
state
.RS 4
Either "present" or "absent", defaults to "present"\&.
.RE
.SH "EXAMPLES"
.sp
.if n \{\
